560\" height=\"315\"><\/iframe><\/p>\n<p>They&#8217;ve got a programme of 10 videos lined up, finishing up with a Twitter Controlled Mood Lamp, which we here at Farset Labs will be really interested to see, considering our occasionally depressed Nabaztag&#8230;<\/p>\n<p>We&#8217;ve been walking a few of the drop-ins through similar circuits, and these videos are going to be a great resource for education. And the Starter packs look pretty darned handy too&#8230;<\/p>\n<p>Disclaimer: Depending on the community response to these videos, we&#8217;re investigating getting a few of the educational packs for the space, so if you&#8217;d be interested in this, PLEASE let us know in the comments section!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Have you wanted to fiddle with electronics but don&#8217;t have the equipment or knowledge?<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":682,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[139],"tags":[474,135,481,134,487,76,12,479,279,480,215,489,488],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/blog.farsetlabs.org.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/680"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/blog.farsetlabs.org.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/blog.farsetlabs.org.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/blog.farsetlabs.org.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/blog.farsetlabs.org.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=680"}],"version-history":[{"count":4,"href":"https:\/\/blog.farsetlabs.org.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/680\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":2344,"href":"https:\/\/blog.farsetlabs.org.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/680\/revisions\/2344"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/blog.farsetlabs.org.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/682"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/blog.farsetlabs.org.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2